name: Kalicha Malabekova
bio: Kalicha is a product delivery manager at a growing startup and IT company in Kazakhstan(remote) and also GDG Bishkek co-lead. She has bachelor's degree in Hardware Engineering from Kyrgyz State Technical University in 2019. Kalicha started her career from being a project manager assistant and she has more than 4 years of successful experience. She also loves to organize IT events, which can help to build the hard IT community in Kyrgyzstan
